com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport

Class Items

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.Items

  • public final class Items
extends Object
    A container for Entitys, EntityPlaceholders, Links, and LinkPlaceholders, which is itself contained by ItemResults and other result containers.

    1.0
